{"tid":1691253,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾馬利生日 「廠」迷贈興：走啦你","createTime":"2019-11-03T14:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T15:01:41.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea93fa2f1832c4e4dfcb93e51ccab90d37a8ce1","tid":1691253,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/5/465/27400085465/27404734653_510x420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F5%2F465%2F27400085465%2F27404734653_510x420.jpg&h=8e63f523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【Now Sports-體育】阿仙奴在官方社交網絡Twitter上發帖，祝賀領隊艾馬利生日，但一眾「廠」迷卻轉移重點。<br />\n<br />\n最近艾馬利（Unai Emery）領「兵」的質素備受質疑，而戰和狼隊之後阿仙奴的聯賽不勝走勢已去到3場，更有傳摩連奴已經蠢蠢欲動，希望接替艾馬利捲土重來。但無論傳聞如何，阿仙奴對於現役領隊當然禮數做足，在他周日的生日大日子，上傳了一張艾馬利的CG繪圖賀卡，送上祝福。<br />\n<br />\n但一眾廠迷似乎不識相，轉載相片但外加hashtag「#EmeryOut」，更大放厥辭：「生日快樂但你要走了。」、「他值得被炒這份生日禮物。」、「給你一張600萬鎊的支票買下合約，並祝你好運。」、「一切完蛋糕就炒掉他吧。」<br />\n<br />\n艾馬利的合約其實到季尾都會完結，暫時阿仙奴一方仍未提出續約的要求，看來無論是「被炒」還是完約離隊，艾馬利在阿仙奴的日子將會買少見少。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片"},{"pid":"03efa4e8a78a488bf5f1a9b4ac11b0a61b66e312","tid":1691253,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:52:34.000Z","msg":"爺爺: 條友真係唔識架喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://media2.giphy.com/media/1xopmJv5fWPtUSZ8Hh/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia2.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1xopmJv5fWPtUSZ8Hh%2Fsource.gif&h=a63e5309&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"945ed149c92e12e17c5bb5c5ce7f617df843645d","tid":1691253,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"賀佢老母"},{"pid":"0f713e78441c6b65a99e9527ffd41e7cc39d87f6","tid":1691253,"uid":34469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:57:56.000Z","msg":"祝愛狗生日快樂<br />\n全家生性病 長命百歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e71aa0c6116f545476a928d59ca7bed86f11fe","tid":1691253,"